   <text>
      <body>
         <div>
            <ab type="salutationType">F2</ab>
            <p rend="right">
               <date when="1945-07-17" cert="high">July 17, 1945</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dr. S. Kracauer<lb/>
               <orgName key="74641">Museum of Modern Art</orgName>
               <lb/>11 West 53rd
            Street<lb/>
               <placeName key="49021">New York</placeName>, <placeName key="50589">N.Y.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
               <emph n="salutation">Dear Dr. <persName key="7721" role="recipient">Kracauer</persName>
               </emph>:</p>
            <p>I am leaving this country<note type="reg">
                  <placeName key="49115">Vereinigte Staaten von
              Amerika</placeName>
               </note> for <placeName key="49050">London</placeName> where I will
          attend meetings of the Board of Governors of <orgName key="74650">Hebrew
            University</orgName> and of the Actions Committee of the <orgName key="74651">World
            Zionist Organization</orgName>.</p>
            <p>From <placeName key="49050">London</placeName> I will proceed to <placeName key="49814">Palestine</placeName>, and hope to be back here again for some months late this
          fall.</p>
            <p>I very much regret that I could not see you any more before my departure, but am looking
          forward to meeting you again after my return.</p>
            <p>
               <emph n="salute">With kindest regards</emph>,</p>
            <p rend="right">
               <emph n="salute">Sincerely yours</emph>,</p>
            <p rend="right">
               <hi rendition="other-hand">
                  <persName key="73655" role="signed">Salman
              Schocken</persName>
               </hi>
               <lb/>
               <unclear>ge</unclear>
            </p>
            <p rend="right">Salman Schocken</p>
            <p>P.S. This letter was dictated by Mr. Schocken but written only after he left.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
